etty@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dolly-parton-miley-nye-getty@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dolly-parton-miley-nye-getty@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dolly-parton-miley-nye-getty@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dolly-parton-miley-nye-getty@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton)</a>发布了她第 49 张个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-partons-rock-album-will-feature-covers-of-prince-the-rolling-stones-led-zeppelin-and-more-3361240">《Rockstar》</a>中的一首新曲目，这是她教女<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus)</a> 2013 年热门歌曲《Wrecking Ball》的新版本。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/miley-cyrus-plastic-hearts-review-pop-superstar-2824255">麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus) – 《塑料心》评论：流行巨星重生为随心所欲的摇滚乐手</a></strong></li></ul><p>帕顿对这首歌的演绎于 10 月 20 日在专辑 11 月 17 日发行之前上传到流媒体平台，赛勒斯在这首歌中的演唱明显更加摇滚。</p><p>在歌曲发行后，帕顿在推特上发表了一份 <a href="https://x.com/DollyParton/status/1715367625885167756?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">声明</a>，他说：“当我听到《Wrecking Ball》时，我几乎在车里哭了。当它开始进入副歌部分时，它就像一个破坏球一样击中了我！”</p><p> “我想一首歌可以有多棒，麦莉·赛勒斯可以有多棒？我想，我必须在我的摇滚专辑中加入这首歌，并且必须让麦莉和我一起唱！我喜欢它，希望你也喜欢，”她补充道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) - Wrecking Ball (音频) ft. Miley Cyrus" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nQMr3VV1u48?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-miley-cyrus-and-dolly-parton-mash-up-wrecking-ball-and-i-will-always-love-you-3373030" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此前，</a>两人曾将《Wrecking Ball》与帕顿的《I Will Always Love You》和<a hr